General.Description: Storskogen Group AB (publ) acquires and operates companies in the areas, such as installation, logistics, infrastructure, engineering services, digital services, HR and competence, industrial technology, automation, and products solutions. The company was founded in 2012 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
